item.description:
POST /api/v3/AIconsultation/{patientId}
GET  /api/v3/AIconsultation-history/{patientId}

Sends the full patient data to ChatGPT and returns an AI clinical consultation.
Each doctor gets 3 trials/month, auto-reset monthly.

